initPathNames

public static void initPathNames(EventReceiver pER)
                          throws DropletException
This is a utility method used by the EventReceiver classes to compute the list of path names and list of dimensions for their current PropertyPath. It theoretically should be a method in each EventReceiver class, but since they don't share a common ancestor, it is here instead.
